    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior maintains a strong shine with only a few minor stone chips on the hood and very light surface scratches consistent with careful driving. Mechanically, it is sound and runs smoothly, with all major systems functioning as intended. The interior is clean and smoke-free, though you will notice some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor scuffing on the floor mats. Overall, this is a solid, dependable car that presents very well and is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
