    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you started? This car is priced to move and offers a great opportunity for someone handy! While it definitely shows its age and will need some mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC to get back to its best, it's a straightforward vehicle with plenty of potential for the right owner. If you're looking for an affordable way to get on the road and don't mind a little elbow grease, this is the one for you!",
      "price": 6500.0,
